
https://www.freebsd.org/doc/handbook/disk-organization.html

Drive Type	Drive Device Name
SATA and IDE hard drives	ada or ad
SCSI hard drives and USB storage devices	da
SATA and IDE CD-ROM drives	cd or acd
SCSI CD-ROM drives	cd
Floppy drives	fd
Assorted non-standard CD-ROM drives	mcd for Mitsumi CD-ROM and scd for Sony CD-ROM devices
SCSI tape drives	sa
IDE tape drives	ast
RAID drives	Examples include 
aacd for Adaptec速 AdvancedRAID, 
mlxd and mlyd for Mylex速, 
amrd for AMI MegaRAID速, 
idad for Compaq Smart RAID, 
twed for 3ware速 RAID.

